<h1 class="doc-page-title">DDT Reports</h1>
<p class="doc-page-lead">Generate comprehensive DDT reports with filtering, analytics, and export capabilities.</p>

<p>Documentation for DDT reports is being developed. This will cover:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Report generation</li>
    <li>Filtering and analytics</li>
    <li>Export capabilities (Excel, PDF, CSV)</li>
    <li>Report scheduling</li>
    <li>Report templates</li>
</ul>

<div class="alert alert-info mt-4">
    <p class="mb-0">For user stories and detailed feature information, see <a href="@Url.Action("UserStories", "Documentation")">User stories</a>.</p>
</div>

